Package: kossyphen
Title: Shared Methods for Kosciuszko Alpine Flowering Phenology
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Will", "Cornwell", email = "wcornwell@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Shared building blocks for analysing the Gibson & Green long-term
    Kosciuszko flowering-walk dataset: raw walk-data ingestion, Australian Plant
    Census name alignment, monthly-temperature loading, onset estimation (Weibull
    limit and first-flower), and per-species temperature-sensitivity fitting.
    Imported by both the observational ("What's in Flower") and the
    experimental/observational synthesis (honours thesis) pipelines so the two
    manuscripts share one method without sharing a pipeline.
